  "title": "Discontinuity Set via Oscillation",
  "root": "",
  "statement": "Let $f:E\\to\\mathbb{R}$. Then\n\\[\nD(f):=\\{x\\in E: f \\text{ is discontinuous at } x\\}\n=\\{x\\in E: \\omega(f;x)>0\\}\n=\\bigcup_{n=1}^{\\infty} \\{x\\in E: \\omega(f;x)\\ge 1/n\\}.\n\\]",
